OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and clear spells expected
OL,7,Fovernight and becoming chilly, with
OL,8,Ftemperatures falling close to freezing
OL,9,Ffor some and a frost likely to develop
OL,10,Fduring the second half of the night.
OL,11,FBreezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FAfter a chilly start, Tuesday
OL,14,Fwill be dry with plenty of sunny
OL,15,Fspells and light winds. Temperatures
OL,16,Fsoon falling again overnight, with
OL,17,Ffrost likely redeveloping.
